div.h1: Column Projection: Finding the Right Field

div.p: Must decode types[0], types[1] first Must sum sizes of preceding columns Projection is O(n) where n = column index
Example: To read column 50, must first decode columns 0-49 to find byte offset

Offset Hex Data Meaning
00-00 0F Header size (15) 01-01 06 Type[0] = INT64 02-02 13 Type[1] = TEXT(3) 03-03 00 Type[2] = NULL 04-0B 00 00 00 2A Col0 = 42 00 00 00 00
0C-11 41 6C 69 63 Col1 = "Alice" 65 00
12-12 (nothing) Col2 = NULL
